data.description: Welcome to your maintenance-free, resort-style Floridian home! Located within the highly coveted, gated Hunter's Green community, this property boasts impeccable pride of ownership, with new landscaping and a concrete driveway. This exquisite home offers three bedrooms, two bathrooms, and a two-car garage. The stainless steel appliances complement the interior, which features tile flooring throughout. The primary bathroom has been tastefully renovated. Enjoy the convenience of a split floor plan, formal living, and formal dining. The primary bathroom has been tastefully renovated.  Hunter's Green is an established master-planned community with no CDD, offering easy access to all major roads and highways while still providing a tranquil neighborhood feel. The HOA includes lawn maintenance and 24-hour manned entrances. Take advantage of the community's abundant amenities, such as tennis courts, a country club, golf course, basketball courts, trails, parks, fitness center, a resort-style pool with lounging areas, and more.  This home is an absolute must-see, so schedule your viewing today!
